data.description: This is an amazing opportunity to purchase a new model home with all the fabulous upgrades - and it comes FULLY FURNISHED! This stunning single-story home has 4 beautifully designed bedrooms, 3 1/2 baths, 2 Fireplaces and a study, two additional flex rooms. The bright kitchen features solid surface countertops, gas range with vent-a-hood, under mount sink, stainless appliances, an island with extended counter for seating, gas cooking, loads of cabinet space, and a walk-in pantry. The kitchen is an open concept connecting with both the family room and the breakfast room for easy entertaining. The primary suite features a large full bath, two separate vanities, a walk-in shower, separate tub, and walk-in closet. The yard is fully landscaped with a sprinkler system, and the large back patio is covered and comes equipped with outdoor fireplace and built in barbecue pit. Home is pre-plumbed with a loop for a water softener. Don't miss this great opportunity to own a fully furnished home with mature landscaping.
